    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The FEA ensemble met pre-established acceptance criteria for all three QoIs. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors achieved the required level. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 1 vs. required Gradation 2) was accepted given that ASTM F1717 prescribes a single standardized test configuration and the regulatory context does not require multi-rate characterization for this device class. The overall credibility is judged sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision.",
